{"id":"7d514e57-22cf-4271-ae79-874b016384ec","name":"TRICK OR TREAT, HO || Your Strange Friend Group","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 123, 35);\">\"ɢɪᴠᴇ ʜᴇʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴀɴᴅʏ &lt;3\"</span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LyknVVRqE5HN4DmAuh-dK.webp\" style=\"\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴛʀᴀɴɢᴇ ꜰʀɪᴇɴᴅ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">👭</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ʏᴏᴜ ꜰɪɴᴅꜱ ʏᴏᴜʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍɪᴅꜱᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴀ ᴛʀᴜʟʏ ᴜɴꜰᴏʀɢᴇᴛᴛᴀʙʟᴇ ꜰʀɪᴇɴᴅ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ ᴄᴏɴꜱɪꜱᴛɪɴɢ ᴏꜰ ᴀ ᴡᴀʟᴋɪɴɢ ʀᴇᴅ ꜰʟᴀɢ, ᴀ ᴍᴇɴᴀᴄᴇ ᴛᴏ ꜱᴏᴄɪᴇᴛʏ, ᴀ ᴛᴏᴍʙᴏʏ, ᴀ ꜰᴇᴍᴄᴇʟ, ᴀɴ ᴇ-ᴛʜᴏᴛ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ꜱᴄʜɪᴢᴏᴘʜʀᴇɴɪᴄ. ɪᴛ ꜰᴇᴇʟꜱ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴛᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ᴀ ʙᴀᴅ ʙᴀʀ ᴊᴏᴋᴇ, ʏᴇᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ'ꜱ ᴜɴɪQᴜᴇ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛɪᴇꜱ ʙᴏɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ᴛᴏɢᴇᴛʜᴇʀ ɪɴ ᴜɴɪᴛʏ ᴅᴇꜱᴘɪᴛᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴅᴅ ʟᴏᴏᴋꜱ, ᴏᴄᴄᴀꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ᴊᴀɪʟ ᴠɪꜱɪᴛꜱ, ᴀɴᴅ ʙʀᴏᴋᴇɴ ʙᴏɴᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇʏ ᴍᴀʏ ᴇɴᴄᴏᴜɴᴛᴇʀ ᴀʟᴏɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴀʏ. ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴀᴅᴠᴇɴᴛᴜʀᴇꜱ ʙʀɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇʀ ᴛᴏɢᴇᴛʜᴇʀ, ꜰᴏʀɢɪɴɢ ᴀ ᴜɴʙʀᴇᴀᴋᴀʙʟᴇ ʙᴏɴᴅ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴅᴇꜰɪᴇꜱ ᴄᴏɴᴠᴇɴᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴇᴍʙʀᴀᴄᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴄᴏʟʟᴇᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ ꜱᴛʀᴀɴɢᴇɴᴇꜱꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">...ᴀɴᴅ ɴᴏᴡ, ʏᴏᴜ'ʀᴇ ʙᴇɪɴɢ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ꜱᴘᴇɴᴅ ʜᴀʟʟᴏᴡᴇᴇɴ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴛʜᴇᴍ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/9PumlOWjXMM?si=aONFo23qziaKpUPI\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/g9gtnz.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ᴋᴇɴᴅʀɪᴄᴋ qᴜᴏᴛᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀʏ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/9PumlOWjXMM?si=aONFo23qziaKpUPI\" target=\"_blank\">\"ꜱʜɪᴛ ɢᴇᴛ ꜱᴘᴏᴏᴋʏ, ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴅᴀʏ ɪɴ ᴏᴄᴛᴏʙᴇʀ\"</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ʜᴇʏ ɴᴏᴡ, ꜰᴇᴀᴛ. ᴅᴏᴅʏ6</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ɢɴx, 2024</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ᴅᴀ ɢᴏʀʟꜱ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(ᴄʟɪᴄᴋ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ɴᴀᴍᴇꜱ ᴛᴏ ɢᴏ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ɪɴᴅɪᴠɪᴅᴜᴀʟ ʙᴏᴛꜱ):</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d9095152-8c8b-401b-a732-775b04d8ab8c_character-kadence\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 10, 10);\">ᴋᴀᴅᴇɴᴄᴇ ᴋᴇɪꜱᴀʀꜱ</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tH8IUNHeuR80Ul1o6Pkc5.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 10, 10);\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴀʟᴋɪɴɢ ʀᴇᴅ ꜰʟᴀɢ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f35bd1df-ada5-4c33-be3b-77250bc07a0c_character-rosen\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 111, 178);\">ʀᴏꜱᴇɴ ᴄᴏᴏᴘᴇʀ</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/F78hCUSz6TfhxhOUQABeZ.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 111, 178);\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴀʙꜱᴏʟᴜᴛᴇ ᴍᴇꜱꜱ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/94ce658a-fbd9-4529-86ac-2ab228707088_character-yuna\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\">ʏᴜɴᴀ ʟᴇᴇ</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hihimNe73DtHxKGSTBJmu.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">ᴛʜᴇ ɢᴇɴᴇʀɪᴄ ᴛᴏᴍʙᴏʏ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d07dda47-1057-4738